OL,3,CCash-strapped council set to receive
OL,4,C#220 million bail-out
OL,6,F#220 million of government money is
OL,7,Fset to be given to a cash-strapped
OL,8,Flocal authority to help it balance its
OL,9,Fbooks.
OL,11,FBradford Council will receive #80
OL,12,Fmillion for the rest of the 2023-2024
OL,13,Ffinancial year, with that sum
OL,14,Fincreasing to #140 million for 2024-
OL,15,F2025.JThe local authority said in
OL,16,FJanuary 2024 that it hoped to receive
OL,17,F'exceptional financial support' from
OL,18,Fthe Government, as it planned to make
OL,19,F#40 million worth of cuts to jobs and
OL,20,Fservices over the next three years.
