OL,6,F"However, this is not free money, it
OL,7,Fhas to be paid back. And like all
OL,8,Fcouncils, we still face extremely
OL,9,Fchallenging financial headwinds over
OL,10,Fthe next few years, primarily due to
OL,11,Frising demand in social care. The
OL,12,Fdifficult decisions have not gone
OL,13,Faway.J"This news does mean, however,
OL,14,Fthat we will be able to put in place
OL,15,Four five year plan to make the council
OL,16,Ffinancially sustainable."
